page.title: 13BILLERICAY NW Trade 1.
page.content: {Queens Park Estate { Queens Park Supermarket}employs 98 members of staff. Most of them are women who work part time. There are 12 cash points and the staff wear a red and cream uniform.{A car park}and small play area adjoin the store. A wide range of food products and general household supplies are on display on the shelves. The store is open 6 days a week from Monday to Saturday. The three busiest days are at the end the week when the store stays open until 8pm. At{Queens Park Roundabout}at the junction with{Perry Street}is situated a general store (food stuffs and household products) and a video shop. The latter premises were, until recently, a builders merchant.
